devtools::install_github("liamgilbey/ggwaffle")
.packages = c("waffle", "ggplot2","aplpack","ggwaffle")
.inst <- .packages %in% installed.packages()
if(length(.packages[!.inst]) > 0) install.packages(.packages[!.inst])
lapply(.packages, require, character.only=TRUE)

Rda waffle paketi, unit graph, waffle graph ve ikon grap iin kullanabiliriz.

Fonksiyon Argumanlar

waffle(parts, rows = 10, keep = TRUE, xlab = NULL, title = NULL,
  colors = NA, size = 2, flip = FALSE, reverse = FALSE, 
  equal = TRUE, pad = 0, use_glyph = FALSE, glyph_size = 12,
  legend_pos = "right")

Arguman aklamalar

waffle(parts, # vektr olarak frekans ya da oranlar. vektrn 2 eleman ve toplam frekans 10 olmamas durumunda 10'a tamamlayacak ekilde 3. eleman eklenir, buna dikkat edilmeli! 2'den fazla eleman olmas durumunda,bu geerli deil. vektr elemanlarnn ismi olmamas durumunda srasyla harfler atanr.
       
       
       rows = 10, # 
       keep = TRUE, frekans olmayan eleman var ise F ile grafikte grntlenmemesi salanr
       xlab = NULL,
       title = NULL, 
       colors = NA, # renkler deitirilmedii srece otomatik olarak atanr
       size = 2, # kareler aras boluk aral
       flip = FALSE, # yerletirme yatay ya da dikey olmas, TRUE olarak atanmasnda 
       reverse = FALSE, 
       equal = TRUE, 
       pad = 0, 
       use_glyph = FALSE, 
       glyph_size = 12, 
       legend_pos = "right")

PseudoData<-data.frame(x1=c(23,43,54,25,12),x2=c("F","F","M","F","M"),x3=factor(c(2,3,3,1,3)))
row.names(PseudoData)<-c("A","B","C","D","E")
waffle(PseudoData$x1)

waffle(table(PseudoData$x2))

library(vcd)
## Loading required package: grid
data("Arthritis")
frekans<-as.data.frame(table(Arthritis$Improved))
veri<-prop.table(frekans$Freq)*100


waffle(c(None=as.integer(veri[1]),100-as.integer(veri[1])), flip = T, colors = c("darkblue","lightgray"), size = 0.2, xlab = paste("Improvement",paste0("%",round(veri[1],2))))

waffle(c(Some=as.integer(veri[2]),100-as.integer(veri[2])), flip = T, colors = c("darkblue","lightgray"), size = 0.2, xlab = paste("Improvement",paste0("%",round(veri[2],2))))

waffle(c(Marked=as.integer(veri[3]),100-as.integer(veri[3])), flip = T, colors = c("darkblue","lightgray"), size = 0.2, xlab = paste("Improvement",paste0("%",round(veri[3],2))))

w<-waffle(c(Marked=as.integer(veri[3]),100-as.integer(veri[3])), flip = T, colors = c("darkblue","lightgray"), size = 0.2,legend_pos = "none", xlab = paste("Marked",paste0("%",round(veri[3],2))))

#
w + annotate("text", x = 5, y = 9, size=5, colour="darkred",label = paste("Marked",paste0("%",round(veri[3],2)))
             )

# https://ggplot2.tidyverse.org/reference/annotate.html#details
  
# adjust margins
w +  theme(plot.background = element_rect(color = 1, size = 1),
        plot.margin = margin(t = 30,  # Top margin
                             r = 30,  # Right margin
                             b = 30,  # Bottom margin
                             l = 30)) # Left margin

library(vcd)
veri2<-waffle_iron(Arthritis,aes_d(group=Improved))
veri2$group<-factor(veri2$group)
ggplot(veri2,aes(x,y,fill=group))+geom_waffle()

ggplot(veri2,aes(x,y,fill=group)) + 
  geom_waffle() +
  coord_equal() +
  scale_fill_waffle() + 
  theme_waffle()
